#ROOM
Vnum     13500
Name     &dThe Deadwind Ravine&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The gloomy trees of Duskwood abruptly die off as you enter this steep,
desolate canyon. The air is unnaturally still and smells of sulfur and
dry dust. The sky above is perpetually choked with dark, swirling clouds.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    13029
Desc      The road back to Duskwood.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    13501
Desc      The path winds deeper into the pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13501
Name     &dThe Desolate Path&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     Shattered boulders and petrified tree stumps litter the sides of the
canyon. The wind whistles eerily through the cracks in the stone. You
feel a profound sense of dread settling over you.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    13500
Desc      The entrance of the ravine.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    13502
Desc      A bridge over a dry riverbed.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 13506 2 13501
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13502
Name     &dDeadman's Crossing&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A crumbling stone bridge spans a deep, completely dry riverbed. Massive
Flesheating Worms occasionally burrow through the cracked earth below,
searching for the corpses of foolish travelers.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    13501
Desc      The desolate path.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    13503
Desc      An ogre campsite.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction down~
ToRoom    13509
Desc      The dry riverbed.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13503
Name     &dThe Ogre Campsite&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A crude, filthy camp set up by the starving Deadwind Ogres. Piles of
gnawed bones and shattered armor are scattered around a smoldering fire.
The brutes here are highly aggressive and desperately hungry.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    13502
Desc      Deadman's Crossing.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    13504
Desc      A dark, reeking cave.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    13505
Desc      The barren valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 13500 2 13503
  Reset E 1 13500 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13504
Name     &dThe Warlock's Cave&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The stench of dark magic is suffocating inside this shallow cave. Ogres
twisted by the corruption of the pass practice destructive fel spells
here, drawing power directly from the tainted earth.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    13503
Desc      The ogre campsite.
~
