#ROOM
Vnum     13505
Name     &dThe Barren Valley&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The canyon widens slightly, revealing a vast expanse of dead, grey dirt.
Nothing grows here. The silence is broken only by the shrieks of the
massive bats diving from the cliffs above.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    13503
Desc      The ogre campsite.
~
