#ROOM
Vnum     13506
Name     &dThe Shadow Web&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The canyon walls here are completely coated in thick, black spider silk.
Mummified remains are suspended high above. This is the hunting ground
of the colossal Shadow Weaver spiders.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    13505
Desc      The barren valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
