#ROOM
Vnum     13507
Name     &dThe Spider's Lair&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The webs are so thick here they block out the sky entirely, creating a
dark, terrifying tunnel. You can hear the skittering of countless eight-
legged horrors moving through the shadows just out of sight.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    13506
Desc      The web-choked gorge.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    13508
Desc      A side path leading back to the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 13508 2 13507
#ENDROOM

