#ROOM
Vnum     13509
Name     &dThe Infested Earth&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     You are standing in the dry riverbed beneath Deadman's Crossing. The
dirt is loose and shifting. Suddenly, the ground erupts as massive,
flesheating worms burst from the soil to attack!
~
Exit
Direction up~
ToRoom    13502
Desc      The bridge above.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 13507 2 13509
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13510
Name     &dThe Fork in the Pass&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The canyon splits here. To the north, a long, treacherous path leads
eventually toward the Swamp of Sorrows. To the south, the canyon widens,
revealing the terrifying, looming presence of Medivh's tower in the
distance.
~
Exit
Direction west~
ToRoom    13505
Desc      The barren valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    13511
Desc      The northern path.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    13512
Desc      The path to Karazhan.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    13508
Desc      The darkened trail.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13511
Name     &dThe Northern Pass&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     This rough path winds northward through the mountains, leading toward the
dismal wetlands of the Swamp of Sorrows. Deadwind Ogres heavily patrol
this route to ambush merchants.
~
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    13510
Desc      The fork in the pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 13500 2 13511
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13512
Name     &dThe Path to Karazhan&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The oppressive aura of dark magic becomes physically heavy here. The sky
is a sickly, swirling purple. The trees are twisted into agonizing shapes.
You are approaching the Guardian's domain.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    13510
Desc      The fork in the pass.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction south~
ToRoom    13513
Desc      The hanging trees.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13513
Name     &dThe Hanging Trees&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The petrified trees here are draped with tattered black cloth and rusted
iron cages. The air is freezing. Restless Phantoms drift through the
branches, mourning their eternal imprisonment.
~
Exit
Direction north~
ToRoom    13512
Desc      The path back to the fork.
~
