Name     &OThe Great Wooden Doors&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You have reached the entrance to the raid. The massive oak doors of
Karazhan are sealed shut by incredibly powerful warding magic, but a 
small crack in the heavy timber allows a brave soul to squeeze through. 
A shimmering magical projection, Medivh's Echo, stands here, eternally 
warning travelers to turn back before the master's madness consumes them too.
~
