Desc     The air inside the Guardian's tower is suffocatingly thick with 
arcane energy. A massive, sweeping staircase climbs into the darkness 
above, while the sounds of a spectral opera echo from the halls. A 
swirling, violet portal dominates the foyer, blocking the path into 
the true depths of the raid.
~
